               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna madḫane ʿālam “Homily on the Saviour of the World” (fols.
                     3ra-10vb)
 II) Maṣḥaf la-tazkāra madḫane ʿālam “Book for the Commemoration
                     of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 10vb-70va)
 III) Malkǝʾa madḫane ʿālam
                     “Image of the Saviour of the World” (fols. 70vb-76ra)
 
 Additio
                     1.</summary>
